_prev_prog_3.Description:
Vertex prevention program includes regular inspection and maintenance in accordance with Process Safety Management and guidelines as published by the Chlorine Institute and the manufacturers of the process equipment.



Vertex also has in place:  

1.  Management System as provided in 68.15 has been installed and verified every third year; 

2.  Employee training for RMP covered process;

3.  Hazard assessment as provided by 68.20-68.42 has been conducted; 

4.  Safety/Security measures, numerous fail-safe measures including automatic shutoff systems on the rail car valves plus facility process valves with automatic sensors, multi-layer systems are in place; 

5.  Procedures/Policies are in place satisfying the prevention requirements of RMP to assure the success of the Vertex Risk Management Program.
